<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9382</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>12027</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟不停地哭着说：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12028</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19893</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“都是我的错。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19894</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22039</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们会找到他的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22040</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24336</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊安慰她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24337</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27392</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们在找兰姆的时候，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27393</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30958</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比发现了一件有趣的事情。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30959</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33984</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“脚印！”他叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38878</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊仔细地研究了那些脚印。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38879</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45130</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后他说：“这个生物可以用两只脚或者四只脚行走。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45131</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48039</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是恐龙带走了兰姆？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48040</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52464</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它如果把兰姆吃了怎么办？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52465</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55047</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>简担心地问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55048</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58508</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们不能再浪费时间了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58509</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61894</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊跟着那些脚印走。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61895</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66305</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这脚印把他们带到了丛林深处。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66306</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70110</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们把每个地方都找遍了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70111</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72917</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但依然没有找到兰姆。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77355</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们精疲力尽地靠在一棵树上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77356</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83770</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们现在要怎么办？”潘瑟抽泣着说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83771</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87162</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，地面开始震动。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87163</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89672</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们看了看彼此。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89673</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91923</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们有点儿害怕。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91924</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94855</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>地面再次抖了抖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94856</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99902</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有个大家伙过来了。”鲍比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99903</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106153</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他们听到了全世界最恐怖的吼声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106154</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109248</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们觉得毛骨悚然。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109249</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114063</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦！哦！”赛伊喃喃自语道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114064</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118527</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那是什么？”简低声问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118528</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122541</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>地面的颤动变得越来越剧烈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122542</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126184</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快跑！”赛伊大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126185</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130310</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们朝着传来声音的反方向跑去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130311</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132311</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不要往回看。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132312</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135719</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊用他最大的声音叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135720</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137931</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但已经太迟了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137932</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143056</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比回过头去看到底是什么在追他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143057</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147918</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那是只暴龙！”他尖叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147919</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152603</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他就被绊倒了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152604</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156288</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>暴龙是牙齿锋利的大恐龙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156289</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160996</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它看上去非常生气，也非常凶残。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160997</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164803</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它离鲍比越来越近了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164804</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170448</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“鲍比！快起来！”潘瑟尖叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170449</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173272</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但鲍比动不了了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173273</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178336</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在那个时候，暴龙停了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178337</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180917</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它看着孩子们身后，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185085</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后又发出了一声巨大的吼声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185086</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189778</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们害怕得捂住了耳朵。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189779</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193795</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>勇敢的赛伊没有捂住耳朵。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193796</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199259</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他想知道是什么让这只恐龙之王停下了脚步。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199260</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205394</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在他们身后，出现了一只巨大的三角龙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205395</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210161</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这只长着三个角的怪物低下了脑袋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210162</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214018</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它已经做好了攻击的准备。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214019</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“暴龙和三角龙要打架了！快走！快走！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218236</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221910</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊向他的兄弟姐妹大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221911</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225601</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们总算安全了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225602</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231242</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它们会杀掉彼此吗？”简哭了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231243</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234376</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那是恐龙生存的方式，简。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234377</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237894</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊试图安慰他的妹妹。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237895</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241446</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在我们必须想想兰姆了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241447</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244490</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们继续奔跑着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244491</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249453</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！”鲍比突然大叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249454</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255448</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！小心！”潘瑟随后也叫了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255449</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259798</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊和简应该听到潘瑟的话了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>259799</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262429</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但他们继续跑着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262430</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>267370</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快他们就跌进了地面上的一个大洞里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>267371</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270973</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这个洞差不多有两米深。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270974</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>277018</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这看上去像个窝。”潘瑟观察着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>277019</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280958</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她拣起了一个光滑的椭圆形的蛋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>280959</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>283729</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它有一个大柚子那么大。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>283730</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287993</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>洞里至少有二十个这样的蛋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287994</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>293321</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你是说，”简倒吸了一口冷气，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>293322</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>297595</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们是在恐龙窝里？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>297596</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>302225</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看上去是这样的。”赛伊回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>302226</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>307305</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“爸爸？”那些蛋里传来了婴儿的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>307306</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>312182</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“兰姆！”潘瑟开心地叫了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>312183</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>316802</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>兰姆不知道怎么来到了这个恐龙窝里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>76</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>316803</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>318507</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你还好吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>77</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>318508</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>323305</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟对她的弟弟表现出了不同以往的关心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>78</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>323306</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>328866</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“妈妈！”兰姆笑着指向了潘瑟身后。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>79</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>328867</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>332385</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟转过身来，开始尖叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>80</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>332386</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>336680</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一只恐龙正在朝着他们冲过来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>81</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>336681</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>339450</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它看上去非常生气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>82</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>339451</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>341831</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那是慈母龙。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>83</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>341832</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>344842</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊浑身发抖地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>84</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>344843</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>349762</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它以为我们要伤害它的孩子。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>85</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>349763</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>354960</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那只恐龙强壮的尾巴来回挥舞着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>86</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>354961</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>361501</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它锋利的爪子已经做好了攻击的准备。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>